These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Hobby: camping, chess, drawing, reading
Flower: zinnia, poppy, daffodil, aconite
1. Hobby:drawing is between Flower:daffodil and Flower:poppy##2
2. Hobby:reading is on the left or right of Flower:daffodil##3
3. Flower:daffodil is not to the left of Flower:daffodil##8
4. Flower:poppy != Hobby:drawing##6
5. Hobby:drawing is somewhere to the right of Hobby:camping##5
6. Hobby:camping is on the right of Flower:zinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | reading  | camping | drawing | chess  |
| Flower   | zinnia | daffodil   | aconite  | poppy |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Food: grapes, tomato, watermelon, zucchini
City: marseilles, rome, paris, prague
1. City:prague is not to the left of City:prague##8
2. Food:grapes is somewhere to the right of Food:zucchini##5
3. Food:grapes == City:rome##1
4. Food:zucchini is between Food:grapes and Food:tomato##2
5. Food:tomato is somewhere between Food:watermelon and City:marseilles##7
6. City:paris is somewhere to the left of Food:tomato##5
7. City:marseilles is not to the left of City:marseilles##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | watermelon | tomato          | zucchini | grapes     |
| City    | paris      | prague | marseilles | rome |

