.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Hobby: magic-tricks, drawing, sudoku, traveling
Movie-Genre: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. Movie-Genre:adventure is not to the left of Hobby:sudoku##8
2. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the far left##1
3. Hobby:drawing is on the right of Hobby:magic-tricks##1
4. Hobby:drawing is in an even position##4
5. Hobby:traveling is on the far left or far right##3
6. Hobby:magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##5
7. Hobby:traveling == Movie-Genre:family##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks | drawing | sudoku     | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

